Filtering

The application of the Kalman filter goes like this:

  • From time series of yty_{t}ytâ€‹, estimate the model parameters.
  • Infer the factors xtâˆ£tx_{t|t}xtâˆ£tâ€‹
  • Simulate xtx_{t}xtâ€‹ using the state equation for ttt in future.
  • Construct the yield curve at ttt using (E:yield-formula).
